HEADWORD: lowball
<hw>lowball</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A poker game in which the
lowest-ranking hand wins.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>lowball</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: lowball
<hw>lowball</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>to give a deceptively low
estimate of the price of (merchandise or services); -- a sales tactic to
induce a person to buy.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> underestimate.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lowbell</ent>⟦br⟧
